data.description: Great home with tons of updates on huge lot in that heart of Marlow! Walk into the huge living room with custom custom built cabinets and Sonance Dolby Atmos surround sound system.  Small nook area off living room with new custom cabinets/bookshelves.  Office space off the dining room with new custom built-in cabinets.  Sun room or multipurpose room off the living room leading out into the backyard with gunite in-ground pool complete with tanning deck and spa as well as an 18x36 shop with 1/2 bath easily accessible from the pool.  Small mud room also leads into the house from backyard adjacent to the kitchen that could easily be expanded into a walk-in pantry. The kitchen has tons of space with soft self-closing doors and drawers, gas 6 burner stove with convection fan, stainless vent hood and dishwasher.  Island complete with bar sink and power underneath.  Granite counter tops throughout. Large master bedroom with walk-in closet.  Two additional bedrooms share a completely remodeled bathroom.  One of the bedrooms is oversized, complete with two separate closet spaces.  Utility room with new custom cabinets and 1/2 bath off of the garage entrance.
